      "title": "Hareen and Manushat resign from the ministry",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign Employment and Labor Minister Mr. Manusha Nanayakkara and Minister of Tourism and Lands Mr. Harin Fernando have decided to resign from their ministerial posts. Through their Twitter account, they announce that they are resigning from their ministerial positions for the appointment of a new interim government."
      ],
